ca.mcgill.ecse428.foodme

Class ControllerTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.mcgill.ecse428.foodme.ControllerTests

  • @SpringBootTest(webEnvironment=RANDOM_PORT)
public class ControllerTests
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves to test controllers methods AppUserController.java, RestaurantController.java, PreferenceController.java Note: Letter is added to assure that tests are executing in alphabetic order The reason why I should be executed in this order is because some tests depend on others Ex. You cannot log out if you haven't sign in a - signup/delete b - authentication/logout c - create/delete/get restaurants d - liked restaurants e - disliked restaurants f - visited restaurants g - preferences h - get all users/restaurants All tests are on user johnsmith (already exists in database)
